{"tid":1313263,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"美國巴打請入，關於聯署要求美國查當地親支組織","createTime":"2019-07-13T17:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T03:43:41.000Z","uid":144626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3aafd79ffaadfa76b872f6ca9f4097d523771696","tid":1313263,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"之前台灣總統English Choi去NY，有一班支持者俾支那當地請嚟嘅打人攻擊<br />\n突顯左美國反支人士言論自由甚至人身安全都受到嚴重威脅<br />\n有見及此，有個在美嘅朋友開左個聯署要求美國政府監視、調查有關親支團體一舉一動<br />\n必要時派FBI/CIA執法取締呢d組織同埋遞解有關人士出境，否則會危害國家安全同埋公民嘅自由<br />\n希望各位在美巴絲支持，多謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-must-investigate-organizations-set-chinese-communist-promote-their-political-agenda?fbclid=IwAR1Mh6T5yuHT7SH0VdyRs_BltbP0d9WilFd5u8NTCU1G-zBw9X6GgjKFn7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Ffederal-government-must-investigate-organizations-set-chinese-communist-promote-their-political-agenda%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Mh6T5yuHT7SH0VdyRs_BltbP0d9WilFd5u8NTCU1G-zBw9X6GgjKFn7E&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=25382b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-must-investigate-organizations-set-chinese-communist-promote-their-political-agenda?fbclid=IwAR1Mh6T5yuHT7SH0VdyRs_BltbP0d9WilFd5u8NTCU1G-zBw9X6GgjKFn7E</a>"},{"pid":"23874e283cbfc4e717e5c1c1b80c87c2721f0a02","tid":1313263,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db5b3c3615c002988877210920bb0d4611d03de6","tid":1313263,"uid":63927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}